items.title: Chartist Talks: Nifty may take a breather now after Record Session Count formation, pick these 2 stocks, says SBI Securities' Sudeep Shah
items.description: The zone of 22,700-22,650 will act as immediate support for the Nifty 50 as the prior swing low and trendline support are placed in that region. On the upside, the 23,200-23,250 will act as a crucial hurdle for the index, said Sudeep Shah.

items.title: Analyst Call Tracker: Trent joins pessimism list, what's souring the sentiment?
items.description: Trent faces mounting pessimism as high valuations, sluggish sales growth, and analyst downgrades cloud its outlook.
